Text:
If you use windows 7, this is the folder to put the .lic file in:

C:\Users\USERNAME\AppData\Roaming\ActiveState,

works perfectly, cheers

!! Be Careful !!

The Keygen contains a Trojan !!

But the license Key (.lic) is apparently functional ...

And the MSI install is the same as founded on the official website (i compared by content byte/byte)
